title: Draconic Bloodline (talent)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Your innate magic comes from [[draconic|dragon]] magic that was
mingled with your blood or that of your ancestors. Choose a [[dragon]] color. You gain [[advantage]] when defending against damage of that dragon's breath weapon type. You also gain [[advantage]] when using social actions with [[dragon]]s.